title: Star Wars Legion Art Show Powered by Neff
description:
http://bit.ly/StarWarsLegionArtShow
Neff teamed up with Disney and Lucas Films to bring the Star Wars Legion Art Show to life. Featuring over 250 custom storm trooper helmets designed by artists from Neff, Lucas Films, and various divisions within Disney. Take a look at the recap from this amazing show.
